@startuml NetPulse_类图_完整_关系用途说明
' =============================================================================
' 完整后端类图：四层 + 关系旁 **中文说明「前者因何使用后者」**
' 与 Spring 注入一致；未画出 PasswordEncoder、InfluxDBClient、Redis 等框架/中间件类型。
' =============================================================================
!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype polyline
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam nodesep 20
skinparam ranksep 24
hide empty methods
top to bottom direction
scale max 2400 width

title NetPulse 后端完整类图（关系旁标注用途说明）

note as READ
  **读图**：实线箭头表示依赖/调用方向，文字说明 **源类为何使用目标类**。
  虚线 **..>** 表示可选注入、ORM 映射或弱依赖。
end note

note as NINF
  **未画出的技术依赖**：**MonitorService / DeviceStatsService / InfluxDbMetricService** 可注入 **InfluxDBClient**；**SnmpStatsService** 使用 **Redis**；**LocalHostStatsService** 使用 **OSHI**；**AuthTokenService** 仅依赖配置密钥。这些不作为类框展开，避免类图过载。
end note

package "控制层（REST 等 HTTP 入口）" #dae8fc {
  class AuthController as "登录认证\nAuthController"
  class UserController as "用户管理\nUserController"
  class RoleController as "角色与菜单权限\nRoleController"
  class DeviceController as "设备 CRUD/探测/采集\nDeviceController"
  class AlertController as "告警规则/历史/通知设置\nAlertController"
  class MetricsController as "仪表盘指标/趋势/刷新\nMetricsController"
  class MetricController as "Influx 折线图数据\nMetricController"
  class HealthController as "健康检查汇总\nHealthController"
  class BatchCommandController as "批量命令下发\nBatchCommandController"
  class AiChatController as "AI 对话与运维助手\nAiChatController"
  class InspectionController as "系统巡检报告\nInspectionController"
  class ConfigBackupController as "配置备份导出\nConfigBackupController"
  class SystemConfigController as "系统参数维护\nSystemConfigController"
  class ApiSettingsController as "大模型 API 等设置\nApiSettingsController"
  class AuditLogController as "审计日志分页查询\nAuditLogController"
  class ExportController as "CSV 导出\nExportController"
  class AlarmRulesController as "告警规则表 CRUD\nAlarmRulesController"
}

package "终端与 WebSocket" #d6eaf8 {
  class SshWebSocketHandler as "浏览器 SSH/Telnet 终端\nSshWebSocketHandler" <<WebSocket>>
}

package "业务与安全服务层" #d5e8d4 {
  class AuthTokenService as "签发/校验登录令牌\nAuthTokenService" <<security>>
  class UserService as "用户与角色分配\nUserService"
  class RoleMenuService as "角色可访问菜单\nRoleMenuService"
  class DeviceService as "设备业务与 Ping 委托\nDeviceService"
  class MonitorService as "定时探测与写状态/时序\nMonitorService"
  class DeviceStatsService as "CPU/内存等指标聚合\nDeviceStatsService"
  class DeviceSshCollectService as "SSH 采集 Linux 指标\nDeviceSshCollectService"
  class DeviceVendorFillService as "定时回填设备厂商\nDeviceVendorFillService"
  class SnmpStatsService as "从 Redis 读 SNMP 指标\nSnmpStatsService"
  class DeviceSnmpCollectService as "网络设备 SNMP 采集\nDeviceSnmpCollectService" <<SNMP>>
  class AlertService as "规则评估与告警历史\nAlertService"
  class AlertEmailService as "告警邮件异步发送\nAlertEmailService"
  class RemediationService as "告警自动修复命令\nRemediationService"
  class AiChatService as "会话/消息与 LLM 调用\nAiChatService"
  class InspectionService as "巡检探测与报告落库\nInspectionService"
  class InspectionScheduleService as "定时生成巡检报告\nInspectionScheduleService"
  class BatchCommandService as "SSH/Telnet 执行单条命令\nBatchCommandService"
  class WebSshService as "终端会话与流转发\nWebSshService"
  class SystemConfigService as "键值系统配置\nSystemConfigService"
  class ConfigBackupService as "多类型 JSON 备份\nConfigBackupService"
  class AuditService as "操作审计异步落库\nAuditService"
  class AuditLogQueryService as "审计条件分页查询\nAuditLogQueryService"
  class InfluxDbMetricService as "按设备查 Influx 指标序列\nInfluxDbMetricService"
  class LocalHostStatsService as "本机 CPU/内存/磁盘\nLocalHostStatsService"
}

package "持久层（JPA Repository）" #fff2cc {
  interface SysUserRepository as "SysUserRepository"
  interface RoleRepository as "RoleRepository"
  interface UserRoleRepository as "UserRoleRepository"
  interface RoleMenuRepository as "RoleMenuRepository"
  interface DeviceRepository as "DeviceRepository"
  interface AlertRuleRepository as "AlertRuleRepository"
  interface AlertHistoryRepository as "AlertHistoryRepository"
  interface AlertTemplateRepository as "AlertTemplateRepository"
  interface AiChatSessionRepository as "AiChatSessionRepository"
  interface AiChatMessageRepository as "AiChatMessageRepository"
  interface InspectionReportRepository as "InspectionReportRepository"
  interface SystemConfigRepository as "SystemConfigRepository"
  interface ConfigBackupRepository as "ConfigBackupRepository"
  interface AuditLogRepository as "AuditLogRepository"
  interface AlarmRulesRepository as "AlarmRulesRepository"
}

package "实体层（领域模型）" #e1d5e7 {
  class SysUser as "SysUser"
  class Role as "Role"
  class UserRole as "UserRole"
  class RoleMenu as "RoleMenu"
  class Device as "Device"
  class AlertRule as "AlertRule"
  class AlertHistory as "AlertHistory"
  class AlertTemplate as "AlertTemplate"
  class AiChatSession as "AiChatSession"
  class AiChatMessage as "AiChatMessage"
  class InspectionReport as "InspectionReport"
  class InspectionItem as "InspectionItem"
  class SystemConfig as "SystemConfig"
  class ConfigBackup as "ConfigBackup"
  class AuditLog as "AuditLog"
  class AlarmRules as "AlarmRules"
}

' ===================== 控制层 → 服务 / 安全 / 仓储 =====================
AuthController --> SysUserRepository : 登录按用户名查账号
AuthController --> UserService : 配合完成登录业务
AuthController --> AuditService : 记录登录成功/失败
AuthController --> AuthTokenService : 生成会话令牌

UserController --> UserService : 用户 CRUD 与角色
UserController --> AuditService : 记录用户变更操作
UserController --> SystemConfigService : 读写用户级通知级别配置

RoleController --> RoleRepository : 读取角色基础数据
RoleController --> RoleMenuService : 维护角色菜单权限

DeviceController --> DeviceService : 设备业务与 Ping
DeviceController --> BatchCommandService : 设备页相关命令能力
DeviceController --> AuditService : 记录设备变更
DeviceController ..> DeviceSnmpCollectService : 可选·触发 SNMP 单机采集

AlertController --> AlertRuleRepository : 规则列表与增删改查
AlertController --> AlertTemplateRepository : 告警模板维护
AlertController --> AlertHistoryRepository : 历史查询与状态更新
AlertController --> DeviceService : 按设备解析规则上下文
AlertController --> AlertEmailService : 读取/保存通知渠道配置
AlertController --> AuditService : 记录告警配置变更

MetricsController --> DeviceService : 取设备列表与在线状态
MetricsController --> DeviceStatsService : 汇总实时/缓存指标
MetricsController ..> SnmpStatsService : 可选·读 Redis 中 SNMP 结果
MetricsController ..> DeviceSshCollectService : 可选·触发 SSH 刷新采集
MetricsController --> LocalHostStatsService : 本机监控页数据

MetricController --> InfluxDbMetricService : 折线图时序查询

HealthController --> DeviceService : 聚合健康状态

BatchCommandController --> BatchCommandService : 多设备执行命令
BatchCommandController --> AuditService : 记录批量命令操作

AiChatController --> AiChatService : 对话与工具调用
AiChatController --> InspectionService : 取巡检摘要供 AI 引用
AiChatController --> AuditService : 记录 AI 相关操作

InspectionController --> InspectionService : 手动巡检与报告查询
InspectionController --> AuditService : 记录巡检操作

ConfigBackupController --> ConfigBackupService : 创建/下载备份
ConfigBackupController --> AuditService : 记录备份行为

SystemConfigController --> SystemConfigService : 维护系统键值配置
SystemConfigController --> AuditService : 记录配置修改

ApiSettingsController --> SystemConfigService : 读写 LLM 等 API 配置
ApiSettingsController --> AuditService : 记录 API 设置变更

AuditLogController --> AuditLogQueryService : 条件分页查询审计

ExportController --> AlertHistoryRepository : 导出告警历史 CSV
ExportController --> AuditLogRepository : 导出审计 CSV

AlarmRulesController --> AlarmRulesRepository : 新版规则表 CRUD
AlarmRulesController --> AuditService : 记录规则表变更

' ===================== WebSocket 终端 =====================
SshWebSocketHandler --> WebSshService : 建立/维护 Shell 会话
SshWebSocketHandler ..> DeviceSshCollectService : 可选·解析终端输出为指标

' ===================== 服务层协作（节选主要用途）=====================
UserService --> SysUserRepository : 用户表 CRUD
UserService --> UserRoleRepository : 维护用户-角色关联
UserService --> RoleRepository : 解析角色编码
UserService --> RoleMenuService : 计算可见菜单、配合保存用户角色

RoleMenuService --> RoleMenuRepository : 读写角色菜单
RoleMenuService --> RoleRepository : 校验角色存在

DeviceService --> DeviceRepository : 设备持久化与查询
DeviceService --> MonitorService : 委托 Ping 与状态刷新

MonitorService --> DeviceRepository : 更新在线状态与 RTT
MonitorService --> AlertService : 设备上下线时评估告警

DeviceStatsService --> DeviceRepository : 遍历待采集设备
DeviceStatsService --> BatchCommandService : 无 Telegraf 时 SSH 取 CPU/内存

DeviceVendorFillService --> DeviceRepository : 查找待补厂商设备
DeviceVendorFillService --> BatchCommandService : SSH 执行 os-release

DeviceSshCollectService ..> WebSshService : 创建临时会话做采集
DeviceSshCollectService --> DeviceRepository : 读取连接信息

DeviceSnmpCollectService --> DeviceRepository : 选取需采集的网络设备
DeviceSnmpCollectService ..> DeviceSshCollectService : 可选·SNMP 失败时回退 SSH

AlertService --> AlertRuleRepository : 加载启用规则
AlertService --> AlertHistoryRepository : 写入/更新告警事件
AlertService --> AlertTemplateRepository : 模板应用（若涉及）
AlertService --> DeviceRepository : 取设备信息与指标评估
AlertService --> AlertEmailService : 触发邮件通知
AlertService --> RemediationService : 触发自动修复
AlertService ..> DeviceSshCollectService : 可选·拉取最新指标
AlertService ..> SnmpStatsService : 可选·读 SNMP 指标

AlertEmailService --> SystemConfigService : 读 SMTP 与通知开关
AlertEmailService --> AlertRuleRepository : 取规则侧通知配置
AlertEmailService --> DeviceRepository : 取设备展示名等
AlertEmailService --> SysUserRepository : 按用户聚合通知级别

RemediationService --> DeviceRepository : 取目标设备连接信息
RemediationService --> BatchCommandService : 在设备上执行修复命令
RemediationService ..> AlertService : 可选·修复后尝试自动结案

AiChatService --> AiChatSessionRepository : 会话持久化
AiChatService --> AiChatMessageRepository : 消息持久化
AiChatService --> DeviceService : 构造设备上下文
AiChatService --> DeviceStatsService : 构造指标上下文
AiChatService --> SystemConfigService : 读取 LLM URL 与 Key
AiChatService ..> DeviceSshCollectService : 可选·补充 SSH 指标
AiChatService ..> SnmpStatsService : 可选·补充 SNMP 指标
AiChatService ..> AlertHistoryRepository : 可选·拉近期告警作上下文

InspectionService --> DeviceRepository : 取待巡检设备列表
InspectionService --> MonitorService : 复用可达性探测
InspectionService --> InspectionReportRepository : 报告与明细落库
InspectionService --> AiChatService : 调用大模型生成巡检结论

InspectionScheduleService --> InspectionService : 定时执行巡检流水线
InspectionScheduleService --> AuditService : 记录定时任务侧审计

BatchCommandService --> DeviceRepository : 按 ID 取 SSH/Telnet 参数

WebSshService --> DeviceRepository : 按设备 ID 取连接参数

SystemConfigService --> SystemConfigRepository : 配置项 CRUD

ConfigBackupService --> ConfigBackupRepository : 备份记录落库
ConfigBackupService --> DeviceRepository : 导出设备 JSON
ConfigBackupService --> AlertRuleRepository : 导出规则 JSON
ConfigBackupService --> SystemConfigRepository : 导出系统配置 JSON

AuditService --> AuditLogRepository : 异步写入审计行

AuditLogQueryService --> AuditLogRepository : 分页与筛选

' ===================== 仓储 → 实体（ORM 映射）=====================
SysUserRepository ..> SysUser : 表 sys_user
RoleRepository ..> Role : 表 role
UserRoleRepository ..> UserRole : 表 user_role
RoleMenuRepository ..> RoleMenu : 表 role_menu
DeviceRepository ..> Device : 表 device
AlertRuleRepository ..> AlertRule : 表 alert_rule
AlertHistoryRepository ..> AlertHistory : 表 alert_history
AlertTemplateRepository ..> AlertTemplate : 表 alert_template
AiChatSessionRepository ..> AiChatSession : 表 ai_chat_session
AiChatMessageRepository ..> AiChatMessage : 表 ai_chat_message
InspectionReportRepository ..> InspectionReport : 表 inspection_report
SystemConfigRepository ..> SystemConfig : 表 system_config
ConfigBackupRepository ..> ConfigBackup : 表 config_backup
AuditLogRepository ..> AuditLog : 表 audit_log
AlarmRulesRepository ..> AlarmRules : 表 alarm_rules

' ===================== 实体关联（业务含义）=====================
SysUser "1" -- "n" UserRole : 用户拥有多角色
Role "1" -- "n" UserRole : 角色分配给多用户
Role "1" -- "n" RoleMenu : 角色对应菜单集合
AlertRule "n" --> "0..1" Device : 规则绑定设备（可全局）
AlertRule "1" --> "n" AlertHistory : 规则触发产生历史
Device "1" --> "n" AlertHistory : 设备上发生的告警
AlertTemplate "1" ..> "n" AlertRule : 模板生成或约束规则
AiChatSession "1" *-- "n" AiChatMessage : 会话包含多条消息
InspectionReport "1" *-- "n" InspectionItem : 报告由明细组成
InspectionItem "n" ..> "1" Device : 明细快照关联设备
SysUser "1" ..> "n" ConfigBackup : 备份记录操作者
SysUser "1" ..> "n" AuditLog : 按用户名关联（非外键）

legend right
  |= 说明 |
  | 本图覆盖 **主要** 注入关系；极少量工具类、AOP、条件 Bean 未展开。 |
  | **MonitorService / DeviceStatsService / InfluxDbMetricService** 对 InfluxDB 的访问在说明中用文字指代。 |
endlegend

@enduml
